headline: Duke Energy: Thank you, Florida customers, for conserving energy during extreme cold on Monday morning
summary: Duke Energy thanks its customers across Florida for reducing their electricity use on Monday morning as extreme cold pushed demand for power higher than normal. Customers' actions helped lessen strain on the electric grid and supported reliable service during one of the coldest mornings of the season.
